<h3>Errors Config</h3>
<p>Only one configurable option exists within the [errors] section of the application.ini file.
The <span class="code"><b>devmode</b> = 0</span> line allows you to enable or disable the code 
trace on Staple error pages. <b>This setting should be off (0) for production servers.</b> 
To turn on the code trace, change this value to 1.</p>  